--------------------------------------------
[Core classes]
--------------------------------------------
- Level
	- Describes obstacle locations
	- Describes start location
	- Describes destination location
	- Describes initial angle position
	- Describes appearance

- It
	- The 'thing' you guide to the destination

- DrawLine
	- The lines a user draws to direct 'It' to the destination
	
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------	
	
Building
- Line-drawing input is handled
- 'START' button exists
- 'POWER' meter exists
- Shoot angle is shown
		
Running
- Line-drawing input is handled
- Ball is shot out at specified angle
- 'START' button disappears
- Power meter disappears
- Shoot angle disappears

LevelWon
- Line-drawing input is disabled
- Remove ball
- Level complete dialog appears

LevelLost
- Line-drawing input is disabled
- Remove ball
- Level failed dialog appears

